flowchart TD
    A[Loop 提交 InvokeRequest] --> B[ProviderRouter]
    B --> C[AdapterRegistry]
    C --> D{adapter kind}
    D -- direct-api --> E[LiteLLMAdapter]
    D -- cli-bridge --> F[Claude/Codex CLI Adapter]
    E --> G[raw response]
    F --> H[response + tool trace]
    G --> I[SchemaValidator]
    H --> I
    H --> J[ToolExecVerifier]
    I --> K{valid?}
    J --> K
    K -- 是 --> L[InvokeResult + usage/evidence]
    K -- 否且有重试 --> M[带错误反馈再次调用]
    M --> I
    K -- 否且耗尽 --> X[fail-closed]
